type BuiltInModelSlug = ModelOptionsByProvider[ProviderKind][number]["slug"];
export type ModelSlug = BuiltInModelSlug | (string & {});
```

#### **keybindings.ts** - Complex Recursive Schemas
```typescript
export const KeybindingCommand = Schema.Union([
